'''Transactional law''' refers to the practice of [[private law]] relating to [[money]], [[business]], and [[commerce]].<ref name="Transactional Law">{{cite web|url=https://www.utexas.edu/law/sao/courses/areas.php?area_id=49&ccyys=20119|title=Transactional Law|publisher=School of Law, University of Texas at Austin|accessdate=2015-07-10}}</ref> Areas of focus include providing legal aid to [[entrepreneur]]s through [[contract]] drafting, [[real estate]] acquisition, and [[intellectual property]] affairs.<ref name="The Transactional Law Clinics">{{cite web|url=http://www.law.harvard.edu/academics/clinical/tlc/|title=The Transactional Law Clinics|publisher=Harvard Law School|accessdate=2015-07-10}}</ref> 

